WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:10.000
Classic "Magdalenas"

00:00:10.000 --> 00:00:13.000
2 large eggs

00:00:13.000 --> 00:00:16.000
60 ml whole milk

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:19.000
Lemon zest

00:00:20.000 --> 00:00:23.000
7 g baking powder, 190 ml sunflower oil

00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:26.000
180 g sugar, 210 g cake flour

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:29.000
A pinch of salt and a pinch of cinnamon

00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:41.000
sift flour and baking powder

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:59.000
Put eggs into the bowl

00:00:59.000 --> 00:01:02.000
Add sugar

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.000
Beat at medium speed

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:15.000
Slow down speed and add milk

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:20.000
Slowly add sunflower oil

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:27.000
Add sifted flour

00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:48.000
Add lemon zest

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:53.000
a pinch of salt...

00:01:55.000 --> 00:01:58.000
and a pinch of cinnamon

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:19.000
Wrap with film

00:02:25.000 --> 00:02:28.000
Refrigerate for two hours 

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:44.000
Beat at medium/high speed

00:02:50.000 --> 00:02:54.000
Put cases in the pan

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:03.000
Fill a pastry bag

00:03:17.000 --> 00:03:21.000
Fill cases at 2/3 of their capacity

00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:38.000
Sprinkle with sugar

